                                                                                                                                                                        R
                                                                                                                                                                    

                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                            		
                                                                                                                                                        

                                                                                                                                                        

                                                                                                                                                            
                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                    Description
                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                            		
                                                                                                                                                            
                                                                                                                                                                

                                                                                                                                                                    

                                                                                                                                                                        Extreme
                                                                                                                                                                        Gradient
                                                                                                                                                                        Boosting,
                                                                                                                                                                        which
                                                                                                                                                                        is
                                                                                                                                                                        an
                                                                                                                                                                        efficient
                                                                                                                                                                        implementation
                                                                                                                                                                        of
                                                                                                                                                                        the
                                                                                                                                                                        gradient
                                                                                                                                                                        boosting
                                                                                                                                                                        framework
                                                                                                                                                                        from
                                                                                                                                                                        Chen
                                                                                                                                                                        &
                                                                                                                                                                        Guestrin
                                                                                                                                                                        (2016)
                                                                                                                                                                        <doi:10.1145/2939672.2939785>.
                                                                                                                                                                        This
                                                                                                                                                                        package
                                                                                                                                                                        is
                                                                                                                                                                        its
                                                                                                                                                                        R
                                                                                                                                                                        interface.
                                                                                                                                                                        The
                                                                                                                                                                        package
                                                                                                                                                                        includes
                                                                                                                                                                        efficient
                                                                                                                                                                        linear
                                                                                                                                                                        model
                                                                                                                                                                        solver
                                                                                                                                                                        and
                                                                                                                                                                        tree
                                                                                                                                                                        learning
                                                                                                                                                                        algorithms.
                                                                                                                                                                        The
                                                                                                                                                                        package
                                                                                                                                                                        can
                                                                                                                                                                        automatically
                                                                                                                                                                        do
                                                                                                                                                                        parallel
                                                                                                                                                                        computation
                                                                                                                                                                        on
                                                                                                                                                                        a
                                                                                                                                                                        single
                                                                                                                                                                        machine
                                                                                                                                                                        which
                                                                                                                                                                        could
                                                                                                                                                                        be
                                                                                                                                                                        more
                                                                                                                                                                        than
                                                                                                                                                                        10
                                                                                                                                                                        times
                                                                                                                                                                        faster
                                                                                                                                                                        than
                                                                                                                                                                        existing
                                                                                                                                                                        gradient
                                                                                                                                                                        boosting
                                                                                                                                                                        packages.
                                                                                                                                                                        It
                                                                                                                                                                        supports
                                                                                                                                                                        various
                                                                                                                                                                        objective
                                                                                                                                                                        functions,
                                                                                                                                                                        including
                                                                                                                                                                        regression,
                                                                                                                                                                        classification
                                                                                                                                                                        and
                                                                                                                                                                        ranking.
                                                                                                                                                                        The
                                                                                                                                                                        package
                                                                                                                                                                        is
                                                                                                                                                                        made
                                                                                                                                                                        to
                                                                                                                                                                        be
                                                                                                                                                                        extensible,
                                                                                                                                                                        so
                                                                                                                                                                        that
                                                                                                                                                                        users
                                                                                                                                                                        are
                                                                                                                                                                        also
                                                                                                                                                                        allowed
                                                                                                                                                                        to
                                                                                                                                                                        define
                                                                                                                                                                        their
                                                                                                                                                                        own
                                                                                                                                                                        objectives
                                                                                                                                                                        easily.
